 />\n&ldquo;The world fully expects that the Chinese government will honor its binding treaty made with the British and registered with the United Nations in which China commits to protect Hong Kong&rsquo;s freedom, legal system, and democratic ways of life,&rdquo;<br />\n國際介入香港，為香港發聲做嘢係以中英聯合聲明呢條國際條約為根基。真係大搖大擺話港獨嘅話你叫其他國家以咩條約為根基介入？樓主嘅論調亦不曾正面回應主張唔用港獨嘅post啲論點"},{"pid":"a615b7809c3ddc2c032a4a998bfbbc1373302fc4","tid":1599382,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a4060ecaab2457862d7d84fb9b7925589ab3be5","tid":1599382,"uid":103936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"076cec90aab9963040b7fe83fea0a7eace4fbfd0","tid":1599382,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"PULL 樓主曾經喺大家達成共識機場要和理非個時嘗試帶風向話要勇武<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXXVgCY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXXVgCY.png&h=5e49c536&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"討論下港獨/機場要行動派 其實冇問題<br />\n問題係 原來樓主咁撚小學雞<br />\n持相反意見就話人5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"我唔想架 個陣咁多post話一定要和理非 我逆向錯咗思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d506cf90a7269075e7276e4480b8c435fed61401","tid":1599382,"uid":278881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fa3bc5e78b37eabcf6d89b198eb0d55d582fd19","tid":1599382,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266ed30c41f7df705661dc0696e4b3fc3d2bcd62","tid":1599382,"uid":278881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n自治係用黎講<br />\n獨立係用黎做<br />\n調轉做咪輸囉<br />\n收皮啦五毛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"咁你可唔可以話比我知點先可以&quot;叫&quot;到人地比自治權我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係睇唔透呀大師 個個都識話自治同港獨冇分別<br />\n但係連最簡單嘅真普選都比唔到 咁點自治 點公投獨立呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class